enry]]'' (2015)\n* ''[[Ghost in the Shell (2017 film)|Ghost in the Shell]]'' (2017)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://netguide.co.nz/story/film-review-ghost-shell-cyberpunk-look-ai-and-mind-hacking/|title=NetGuide NZ - Film review: Ghost in the Shell - a cyberpunk look into AI and mind hacking |first= Sara|last= Barker|work=NetGuide NZ}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.heise.de/newsticker/meldung/Ghost-in-the-Shell-Die-Renaissance-des-Cyberpunk-3668390.html|title=Ghost in the Shell: Die Renaissance des Cyberpunk |first=Volker|last=Briegleb|work=heise online}}</ref>\n* ''[[Blade Runner 2049]]'' (2017)\n* ''[[Bleeding Steel]]'' (2017)\n* ''[[Ready Player One (film)|Ready Player One]]'' (2018)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.neondystopia.com/cyberpunk-movies-anime/spielberg-returns-to-cyberpunk-with-ready-player-one/|title=Spielberg Returns To Cyberpunk With Ready Player One|author=Shadowlink|date=May 3, 2018|website=Neondystopia.com|access-date=December 15, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Schwartz|first=Jack|date=April 4, 2018|title=Ready Player One: 'Ready Player One' wins with CGI and a nostalgic essence|url=https://dailytrojan.com/2018/04/04/ready-player-one-ready-player-one-wins-with-cgi-and-a-nostalgic-essence/|work=Daily Trojan|access-date=December 15, 2018}}</ref>\n* ''[[Upgrade (film)|Upgrade]]'' (2018)\n* ''[[Hotel Artemis]]'' (2018)\n* ''[[Alita: Battle Angel]]'' (2019)\n* ''[[Altered Carbon: Resleeved]]'' (2020)\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Animation===\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n* ''[[Megazone 23]]'' (1985)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.scifi.com/sfw/anime/sfw11389.html |title=Megazone 23 &#124; Anime Reviews &#124; SCI FI Weekly |publisher=Scifi.com |date=2004-09-07 |accessdate=2009-02-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090422135156/http://www.scifi.com/sfw/anime/sfw11389.html|archivedate=22 April 2009}}</ref>\n* ''[[Neo Tokyo (film)|Neo Tokyo]]'' (1986)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/movie/221844/moviemain.jhtml |title=Neo-Tokyo &#124; F