aku/>\n* ''[[Osman (video game)|Osman]]'' (1996)<ref name=kotaku/>\n* ''[[Blade Runner (1997 video game)|Blade Runner]]'' (1997)<ref>{{cite news |title= The Ten Best Film to Game Adaptations: Blade Runner (PC) |first=Michael |last=Plant |work=[[The Independent]] |date= 14 May 2009 |accessdate= March 21, 2010 |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/gaming/the-ten-best-film-to-game-adaptations-1684974.html?action=Popup&ino=4 | location=London}}</ref>\n* ''[[Final Fantasy VII]]'' (1997)<ref>{{cite news|last=Li|first=Kenneth|title=Flash Fantasy On A Role|url=http://articles.nydailynews.com/1997-09-07/news/18052526_1_role-playing-final-fantasy-vii-turn-based|work=[[Daily News (New York)|New York Daily News]]|accessdate=2 October 2011|date=September 7, 1997}}</ref>\n* ''[[Ghost in the Shell (video game)|Ghost in the Shell]]'' (1997)<ref name=kotaku/>\n* ''[[Xenogears]]'' (1998)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thegamescouts.com/2012/07/scouting-classics-xenogears.html|title=Scouting Classics: Xenogears|publisher=The Game Scouts|access-date=2015-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160812143517/http://www.thegamescouts.com/2012/07/scouting-classics-xenogears.html|archive-date=2016-08-12|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n* ''[[Deus Ex]]'' series\n** ''[[Deus Ex (video game)|Deus Ex]]'' (2000)<ref>{{cite web | url=http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/Technology/Return-To-Classic-Form/Article/200403313017586?lid=ARTICLE_13017586_Return%20To%20Classic%20Form?&lpos=searchresults | title=Return To Classic Form? &#124; Technology &#124; Sky News | publisher=News.sky.com | date=2004-03-18 | accessdate=2009-02-05}}</ref>\n** ''[[Deus Ex: Invisible War]]'' (2003) <ref>{{cite news|title=Deus Ex 2: Invisible War Review|url=http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/deusex2/index.html|date=2004-03-21}}</ref>\n** ''[[Deus Ex: Human Revolution]]'' (2011) <ref>{{cite news|title=Deus Ex: Human Revolution Review|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/technology/video-games/game-reviews/review-a-game-for-the-thinking-cyberpunk/article2150301/|date=2011-09-02|accessdate= 2011-09-04|location=Toronto|work=The Globe and Mail|first=Chad|last=Sapieha}}</ref>\n** ''[[Deus Ex: The Fall]]'' (2013)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2013-06/07/deus-ex-the-fall-preview/viewgallery/304906 |title=Gallery Image: Deus Ex: The Fall |magazine=Wired |accessdate=2014-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211201642/http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2013-06/07/deus-ex-the-fall-preview/viewgallery/304906 |archive-date=2013-12-11 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n** ''[[Deus Ex: Mankind Divided]]'' (2016)\n* ''[[Oni (video game)|Oni]]'' (2001)<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/gamesblog/2014/jan/22/30-greatest-video-games-that-time-forgot|title=The 30 greatest video games that time forgot|first=Keith|last=Stuart|date=22 January 2014|publisher=|newspaper=The Guardian}}</ref>\n* ''[[Uplink (video game)|Uplink]]'' (2001)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.introversion.co.uk/uplink/articles/player2playerarticle.html |title=Uplink |publisher=Introversion.co.uk |accessdate=2009-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081116135358/http://www.introversion.co.uk/uplink/articles/player2playerarticle.html |archive-date=2008-11-16 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Tito |first=Greg |url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/issues/issue_13/84-Someday-Ill-Hack-the-Gibson |title=The Escapist : Someday, I'll Hack the Gibson |magazine=Escapistmagazine.com |date=2005-10-04 |accessdate=2009-02-05}}</ref>\n* ''[[Breath of Fire: Dragon Quarter]]'' (2002)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/02/12/breath-of-fire-dragon-quarter-2|title=Breath of Fire: Dragon Quarter|first=By Jeremy|last=Dunham|publisher=}}</ref>\n* ''[[.hack]]'' series\n** ''[[.hack (video game series)|.hack//IMOQ]]'' (2002\u20132003)\n** ''[[.hack//G.U.]]'' (2006\u20132007)\n** ''[[.hack//Link]]'' (2010)\n* ''[[Neocron]]'' (2002