90109203314/http://www.kfccinema.com/reviews/action/burstcity/burstcity.html |archivedate=2009-01-09 }}</ref>\n* ''[[Tron]]'' (1982)<ref>{{cite news|title=THE EVOLUTION OF CYBERPUNK |url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F0CEFDE1330F93BA3575BC0A965958260&sec=technology&spon=&pagewanted=all | date=1993-08-08|accessdate= 2009-02-17 | work=The New York Times | first1=Nick | last1=Ravo | first2=Eric | last2=Nash}}</ref>\n* ''[[Brainstorm (1983 film)|Brainstorm]]'' (1983)<ref>{{cite news|last=Ravo |first=Nick |url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F0CEFDE1330F93BA3575BC0A965958260&sec=technology&spon=&pagewanted=all |title=The Evolution Of Cyberpunk |newspaper=New York Times |date=1993-08-08 |accessdate=2009-02-28}}</ref>\n* ''[[Videodrome]]'' (1983)<ref>{{cite web|author=|url=http://www.channel4.com/film/reviews/film.jsp?id=109880&section=review&page=all |title=Videodrome Movie Review (1983) from Channel 4 Film |publisher=Channel4.com |accessdate=2009-02-05}}</ref>\n* ''[[The Terminator]]'' (1984)\n* ''[[RoboCop]]'' (1987)<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Elmer |first=Philip |url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,977654-2,00.html |title=Cyberpunk! |magazine=TIME |date=1993-02-08 |accessdate=2009-02-05}}</ref>\n* ''[[The Running Man]]'' (1987)\n* ''[[Gunhed (film)|Gunhed]]'' (1989)<ref>{{cite web|title=Gunhead B-Movie Review|url=http://www.badmovies.org/movies/gunhed/|accessdate= 2009-02-05}}</ref>\n* ''[[Circuitry Man]]'' (1990)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thespinningimage.co.uk/cultfilms/displaycultfilm.asp?reviewid=2330 |title=Circuitry Man Review (1990) |publisher=Thespinningimage.co.uk |accessdate=2009-02-05}}</ref>\n* ''[[Hardware (film)|Hardware]]'' (a.k.a. ''M.A.R.K. 13'') (1990)<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/hardwarerharrington_a0aaf1.htm |title=Hardware |publisher=Washingtonpost.com |date=1990-09-14 |accessdate=2009-02-05}}</ref>\n* ''[[Megaville]]'' (1990)<ref>{{cit