oll |url=http://www.theherald.co.uk/search/display.var.1747920.0.metal_psydoll.php |accessdate=2009-02-04 }}{{dead link|date=June 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n* [[Sigue Sigue Sputnik]]<ref>{{cite web|title=sigue_sigue_sputnik|url=http://www.absoluteradio.co.uk/music/artists/sigue_sigue_sputnik/biography/|accessdate=2009-02-04|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110807135528/http://www.absoluteradio.co.uk/music/artists/sigue_sigue_sputnik/biography/|archivedate=2011-08-07}}</ref>\n* [[Starset]] \n* [[Voivod (band)|Voivod]]<ref>{{cite journal|last=Davis|first=Erik|authorlink=Erik Davis|date=February 1990|title=Long live the new flesh|journal=[[Spin (magazine)|Spin]]|volume=5|issue=11|page=59|issn=0886-3032}}</ref>\n* [[Yellow Magic Orchestra]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Lester|first=Paul|title=Yellow Magic Orchestra|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2008/jun/20/culture.electronicmusic|work=[[The Guardian]]|accessdate=26 May 2011|date=20 June 2008|location=London}}</ref>\n* [[Nero (band)|Nero]]\n* [[Perturbator]]\n\n;Releases\n\nSister by Sonic Youth\n\nDaydream Nation by Sonic Youth\n\n* ''[[Blade Runner (soundtrack)|Blade Runner]]'' by [[Vangelis]]<ref>{{cite web|title=The classic soundtrack gets filled out and polished up with extras on the side|url=http://www.subba-cultcha.com/article_album.php?id=6627|accessdate= 2009-02-06}}</ref>\n* ''[[Cyberpunk (album)|Cyberpunk]]'' by [[Billy Idol]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chaoscontrol.com/content_article.php?article=billyidol |title=Billy Idol |accessdate=2008-08-12 |last=Gourley |first=Bob |work=Chaos Control Digizine |publisher=Bob Gourley |year=1993 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071009124523/http://www.chaoscontrol.com/content_article.php?article=billyidol |archivedate=2007-10-09 }}</ref>\n* [[Drezden (Drezden album)|''Drezden'']] by [[Drezden (band)|Drezden]]<ref name=\"km\" />\n* ''[[Outside (David Bowie album)|Outside]]'' by [[David Bowi